window.__KB.push({"t": "Policy No. 保单编号： CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE - CANCER 重病保障索偿表格 － 癌 症 PART II – ", "f": "C10_S_(12_2024).pdf", "s": "Policy No. 保单编号： CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE - CANCER 重病保障索偿表格 － 癌 症 PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部分 – 本应诊医生报告必须由受保人自费聘请之合资格注册医生填写 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份证号码 3. Age 年龄 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 阁下是否病人之私人医生？  No 否  Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，请填写有关资料。 Period of Consultation (DD/MM/YYYY) 应诊期间（日/月/年） Past Health History 病人过往健康情况 5. a) Date on which you first attended the patient for this disease (Cancer). 首次为病人诊治是项病症（癌症）之日期。(DD日/MM月/YYYY年) b) How long had the patient been experiencing the symptoms/complaints before the first consultation? 病人在首次求诊前已患有症状／主诉多久？(DD日/MM月/YYYY年) c) Symptoms (s) / complaint(s) of the patient relating to this disease (cancer) 病人就是项病症（癌病）所出现的症状/主诉 d) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何时通知病人诊断结果？（请填写准确日期）(DD日/MM月/YYYY年) 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 请详尽填写明确诊断资料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人过往曾否患有上述疾病或有关疾病？  No 否  Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 如果「有」，请填写明确诊断资料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) and /or Hospital(s) Date of Consultation (DD/MM/YYYY) 应诊医生姓名及/或医院名称 诊治日期（日/月/年） Address(es) 地址 Exact Diagnosis 明确诊断资料 8. Is there anything in the patient's family history which would have increased the risk of Cancer? 病人的家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上癌症机会的事项？ n No 否 n Yes 有 If \"Yes \", give details 如果「有」，请填写有关资料。 9. Did or does the patient have any habits in relation to drinking, drug taking and smoking. 病人是否或曾有饮酒、吸毒或吸烟的习惯？ Duration 持续时间 From 从 (DD日/MM月/YYYY年) To 至 (DD日/MM月/YYYY年) Consumption Per Day 每天用量： a) Drinking 饮酒 n No 否 n Yes是 b) Drug taking 吸毒 n No 否 n Yes是 c) Smoking 吸烟 n No 否 n Yes是 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人寿保险（国际）有限公司 C10_S (11/2025) 1 of 3 Policy No. 保单编号： 10.a) What was the site or organ involved and the precise histology of the tumor? 请填写肿瘤所处的位置或受影响的器官，和详列肿瘤的组织结构? b) What tests were performed to confirm the diagnosis? 进行了哪些测试来确认此诊断？ Date of the Test 检验日期 (DD日/MM月/YYYY年) Test item 检验项目 Result 结果 c) What was the staging system used? 肿瘤的分期系统? (For cancer, pleases state stage under the American Joint Committee on Cancer (AJCC) cancer staging system; for brain tumour, please state stage under World Health Organization Classification of Tumours; for Hodgkin lymphoma or Non-Hodgkin lymphoma, please state stage under the Lugano classification; for chronic lymphocytic leukaemia, please stage the Rai stage) (如属癌症，请根据美国癌症联合委员会 (American Joint Committee on Cancer) 癌症分期系统分类列出其级别 ;如属脑肿瘤，请根据世界卫生组织肿瘤分类 (WHO Classification of Tumours）列出其级别）; 如属何杰金淋巴瘤或非何杰金淋巴瘤，请根据卢加诺分期法 (Lugano Classification）列出其级别; 如属慢性淋 巴球白血病，请列出其Rai级别 d) Based on above staging system, what is the staging of the tumour? 根据以上分期系统，该肿瘤为第几级别? e) Is the disease completely localized? 病症是否完全局部化？ f) Is there uncontrolled growth and spread of malignant cells? 癌细胞是否不受控制地生长和扩散？ g) Is there an invasion and destruction of adjacent tissue by malignant cells? 癌细胞是否侵入和破坏邻近细胞组织？ h) Are regional lymph nodes involved? 是否影响邻近淋巴结？ i) Are there distant metastases? 是否距离性转移？ n No 否 n No 否 n No 否 n No 否 n No 否 n Yes是 n Yes是 n Yes是 n Yes是 n Yes是 11. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 请提供曾为病人诊治是项病症的医生资料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available （) 敬请提供任何有关医疗报告副本） Name of Physician(s) and /or Hospital(s) 医生姓名及／或医院名称 Address(es) 地址 Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) (DD/MM/YYYY) 诊治及／或留院日期（日/月/年） 12. What kind of treatment(s) is/are the patient receiving/had the patient received? 病人正／曾接受什么治疗? Treatment 治疗 Please list out the treatment dates, period, schedule and details of treatments 请列出治疗日期、期间、时间表和治疗详情 (DD日/MM月/YYYY年) n Surgery 手术 n Radiotherapy 电疗 n Chemotherapy 化疗 n Targeted therapy 标靶治疗 n Bone marrow transplant 骨髓移植 n Proton therapy 质子治疗 n Immunotherapy 免疫治疗 n Cyber knife 数码导航刀 n Gamma knife 伽玛刀 n CAR-T cell infusion 嵌合抗原受体T细胞(CAR-T) 细胞滴注 n Hyperthermia therapy 高温热疗 n Photodynamic therapy (PDT) 光动力疗法(PDT) n Stem cell therapy 干细胞治疗 n Clinical trial cancer drug treatment 临床试验癌症药物治疗* n Off-label cancer drug treatment 非适应症癌症药物治疗* n Others, please specify 其他，请注明: * Please answer question 14 if patient is receiving/had received Clinical Trial Cancer Drug Treatment and/or Off-label Cancer Treatment 如病人正／曾接受「临 床试验癌症药物治疗」及/或「非适应症癌症药物治疗」，请回答问题14 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人寿保险（国际）有限公司 C10_S (11/2025) 2 of 3 Policy No. 保单编号： 13. Is the patient receiving End-of-life Care treatment? (ie. any treatment provided in hospital or a registered hospice specifically to relieve cancer symptoms in which the cancer is progressing due to lack of treatment to cure or control the cancer) 病人是否正接受晚期护理?（即在医院或注册善终院舍接受舒缓癌症症状的 治疗，而该癌症正在恶化且未有医治或控制该癌症的治疗方法） n No 否 n Yes 是 If \"Yes \", please advise details of previous treatments given, current situation, prognosis and periods that the patient receives End-of-life Care treatment 如果是，请就曾提供的治疗、现时情况、预后和病人接受晚期护理治疗的时段提供更多详情 14. If patient is receiving/had received Clinical Trial Cancer Drug Treatment and/ or Off-label Cancer Drug Treatment, please provide the following documents. 如病 人正／曾接受「临床试验癌症药物治疗」及/或「非适应症癌症药物治疗」，请提供以下文件: - Medical journal 医学文献 - Clinical practice guidelines or protocol stipulated by a medical institution 医疗机构规定的临床实践指南或方案 - Drug insert 药物说明书 15. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 阁下认为有否其他资料可协助 本公司审核是项索偿申请？请提供有关资料。 Name of Physician (with stamp) 医生姓名（连印章） Qualification of Physician 医生资格 Address 地址 Signature 签署 Date 日期 (DD日/MM月/YYYY年) Tel. No. 电话号码 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人寿保险（国际）有限公司 C10_S (11/2025) 3 of 3"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "APPLICATION FOR COMPASSIONATE ASSISTANCE PROGRAM 保單恩恤援助申請書 PART I: APPLICATION F", "f": "C16.pdf", "s": "APPLICATION FOR COMPASSIONATE ASSISTANCE PROGRAM 保單恩恤援助申請書 PART I: APPLICATION FORM 第一項：申請表 1. POLICY NO. 保單號碼 *2. AMOUNT OF LOAN REQUEST 申請貸款額 Branch code 分行編號 Advisor code 保險顧問編號 Advisor’s name 保險顧問姓名 Contact no. 聯絡電話 Location 地點 3. LIFE INSURED 受保人 FULL NAME 姓名 ADDRESS 地址 CHINESE NAME 中文姓名 TEL NO. 電話號碼 4. OWNER OF THE POLICY (COMPLETE IF OTHER THAN LIFE INSURED) 保單持有人（如等同於受保人則無需填寫此欄） FULL NAME 姓名 CHINESE NAME 中文姓名 TEL NO. 電話號碼 ADDRESS 地址 5. BENEFICIARY 受益人 FULL NAME 姓名 RELATIONSHIP TO LIFE INSURED 與受保人之關係 6. PAYMENT INSTRUCTIONS 付款指示 □ Cheque Payment 以支票形式付款 Cheque Currency (a) (for USD policy only) 支票幣值 (a（) 只適用於美元保單） □ USD Cheque (drawn in Hong Kong) 美元支票（由香港的銀行付款） □ USD Cheque (drawn in United States) 美元支票（由美國的銀行付款） □ HKD Cheque (b) 港元支票 (b) Notes 註: (a) In general, it takes a longer settlement period to clear a foreign cheque in Hong Kong. Bank charges may be incurred by client for clearing the cheque. 銀行通常需要較長的結算時間於香港兌現外幣支票；另銀行或會向客戶徵收兌現支票的相關手續費。 (b) The HKD equivalent will be based on the currency exchange rate provided by the Company at the time of issue of the cheque and it can be changed from time to time. 相等之港元將會以支票發出時的貨幣兌換率計算，而宏利將不時提供有關的貨幣兌換率。 * REMARKS: THE LOAN AMOUNT IS SUBJECT TO MANULIFE FINAL APPROVAL. 注意：援助貸款額以宏利保險最後批核為準。 The Chinese version of this form is for reference only. In the event of conflicts between the Chinese and the English versions, the English version shall prevail. 此表格之中文譯本只供參考之用，若與英文有異，一概以英文為準。 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C16 (11/2025) 1 of 3 Declaration and Authorization 聲明及授權 I/We hereby declare that the answers to the above questions are full and true to the best of my/our knowledge. I/We further authorize any physician, hospital, insurance company, claims investigation company, government authority or organization that has any record or knowledge of me/us, my/our health or my/our activities (including records relating to Social Welfare, Workers’ Compensation, credit, financial, earnings and employment history) to furnish to Manulife (International) Limited (“Manulife”) or its authorized representative such information including without limitation all information with respect to any illness or injury, medical history, consultation, prescription or treatment and copies of all hospital or medical records. A photostatic copy of this authorization shall be as effective and valid as the original. 本人／我們特此聲明填報於本表格內之資料已是本人／我們所知之全部並為真實無訛。本人／我們茲授權任何醫生、醫院、保險公司、賠償調查公司、政府有關部門或其他持有本人／我們個人資料、健康狀 況或記錄（包括有關本人／我們所獲之社會福利及勞工賠償、本人／我們之存款、財政狀況、入息及就業記錄）之組織可以將該等資料，包括但不限於所有有關本人／我們之疾病或受傷，傷患之病歷、診斷報 告、藥方或治療及所有醫院或醫療記錄副本等資料予宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司（“宏利”）或其代理人。此授權書之複製本與正本具同等效力。 Personal Information Collection Statement 個人資料收集聲明 I/we acknowledge that the personal data provided in this Form will be used by Manulife for the purposes of processing, adjudicating and investigating claims application(s) and request(s) for credit service, approving and underwriting insurance applications, administering and reinsuring policies, complying with applicable laws and other related purposes and for such purposes, may be transferred to such persons or entities (whether within or outside Hong Kong) as: (a) any person in connection with any claims made by or against or otherwise involving customers in respect of any products and/or services; (b) any agent, contractor or third party service provider who provides administrative, telecommunications, computer, information technology, payment, data processing or storage, marketing, mailing, printing, telemarketing, customer satisfaction analysis, or other services to Manulife or any member of Manulife's group of companies in connection with the operation of business, including any custodian, administrator, investment manager, investment advisor or distributor; (c) any credit reference agencies or, in the event of default, any debt collection agencies; (d) any advisor (including his or her employees) or other intermediary (including their employees); (e) reinsurers and medical service providers; (f) employers of the customers; (g) any person which has undertaken to Manulife or any member of Manulife's group of companies to keep such data confidential; (h) any actual or proposed assignee, transferee, participant or sub-participant of the rights or business of Manulife or any member of Manulife's group of companies ; (i) any member of Manulife's group of companies; (j) any person to whom Manulife or any member of Manulife's group of companies is under an obligation or otherwise required to make disclosure under the requirements of any law, rules, regulations, codes of practice, guidelines or guidances binding on or applicable to Manulife or any member of Manulife's group of companies including but not limited to any local or foreign regulators, governmental bodies, or industry recognised bodies; (k) any person to whom Manulife or any member of Manulife's group of companies is under an obligation or otherwise required to make disclosure pursuant to any contractual or other commitment or arrangement with local or foreign regulators, governmental bodies, or industry recognised bodies (whether within or outside Hong Kong) that is assumed by or imposed on Manulife or any member of Manulife's group of companies by reason of its financial, commercial, business or other interests or activities in or related to the jurisdiction of the relevant local or foreign regulators, governmental bodies, industry recognised bodies. I/we understand that I/we am/are not obliged to provide such personal data as requested but if I/we refuse to provide such data, Manulife may not be able to proceed further on my/our application(s) and/or request(s) in this Form. I/we may request access to and correction of my/our personal data held by Manulife, by writing to Privacy Officer at Manulife (International) Limited, 22/F., Tower A, Manulife Financial Centre, 223-231 Wai Yip Street, Kwun Tong, Kowloon, Hong Kong. 本人／我們確認載於本表格內之個人資料將被宏利用以處理、判定及調查有關之索償及代繳費用服務申請，批核及承保保險申請，管理保單並安排"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "Policy No. 保單編號： CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE - TOTAL AND PERMANENT DISABILITY 重", "f": "C22.pdf", "s": "Policy No. 保單編號： CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE - TOTAL AND PERMANENT DISABILITY 重病保障索償表格 - 完全及永久傷殘 PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？  No 否  Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation (DD/MM/YYYY) 應診期間(日/月/年) Past Health History 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which you first attended the patient for this disease (Total and Permanent Disability). 首次為病人診治是項病症（完全及永久傷殘）之日期。 b) What was the symptom(s) experienced prior to the first consultation? 病人首次求診前有何症狀？ c) How long had the patient been experiencing the symptom(s) before the first consultation? 病人在首次求診前已患有症狀多久? d) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果？（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. What kind(s) of disability do(es) the patient suffer from? 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。病人患有哪種傷殘？ 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？  No 否  Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫確實診斷資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) and /or Hospital(s) Date of Consultation (DD/MM/YYYY) 應診醫生姓名及/或醫院名稱 診治日期(日/月/年) Address(es) 地址 Exact Diagnosis 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient's family history which would have increased the risk of Total and Permanent Disability? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上完全及永久傷殘機會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C22 (11/2025) 1 of 2 Policy No. 保單編號： 10. Which of the following daily activities and the period is he/she NOT able to perform as a result of the disability? If the activity can be performed by using special equipment, then he/she is considered able to perform that activity. 他/她因殘疾而無法進行哪些日常生活之活動以及相關的時段? 若相關的日常生活之活動可通過使用特殊設 備進行仍可視為他/她能夠進行該活動。 If NOT able to perform below daily activities as a result of the disability, please tick below box(es) 如因殘疾而無法進行下列日常生活之活動, 請於以下的方格內填上“✓” 號 Period not able to perform as a result of the disability 因殘疾而無法進行此活動的時段 (DD日/MM月/YY年)  A) Washing - the ability to wash in the bath or shower (including getting into and out of the bath or shower) or wash satisfactorily by other means. 沐浴 － 浸浴或淋浴方式自我清洗（包括能進入及離開 浴缸或淋浴間）或以其他方式達到滿意自我清洗的能力。  B) Dressing - the ability to put on, take off, secure and unfasten all garments and, as appropriate, any braces, artificial limbs or other surgical appliances. 更衣 － 穿戴並固定及解開並脫下所有衣物及 任何矯正器、義肢或其他醫學用支架(視何者適用而定)的能力。  C) Transferring - the ability to move from a bed to an upright chair or wheelchair and vice versa. 行 動 － 從床移動至直立的椅子或輪椅上的能力，反之亦然。  D) Mobility - the ability to move indoors from room to room on level surfaces. 移動 － 於平坦地面之室 內由一個房間移動到另一房間的自由活動能力。  E) Toileting - the ability to use the lavatory or otherwise manage bowel and bladder functions so as to maintain a satisfactory level of personal hygiene. 如廁 － 自行如廁或能自我控制肛門及膀胱功能， 以保持合理程度之個人衛生的能力。  F) Feeding - the ability to feed oneself once food has been prepared and made available. 進食 － 自 行進食預先準備妥當及獲提供之食物的能力。 11. Is the patient suffered from total and permanent disability? If yes, how long has the patient suffered from this disability. If not, please explain. 病人是否完全及永久傷殘？如是，病人的傷殘情況已持續多久？如否，請加以說明。 12. Is the disability permanent in nature? 病人是否屬永久傷殘？ 13. In your professional opinion, is the patient unable to perform any work for remuneration or profit? If yes, please explain. 根據閣下的專業意見，病人是否無法從事任何可獲報酬或利潤之職業或工作？如是，請加以說明。 14. Please give details of radiological investigations, M.R.I., C T scan, laboratory evidence and any other test results for reference. 請提供放射檢驗、磁力共振、電腦斷層掃描、實驗室證據或其他檢驗結果的詳情以供參考。 15. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 請提供曾為病人診治是項病症之醫生資料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available ) （敬請提供任何有關醫療報告副本） Name of Physician(s) and /or Hospital(s) 生姓名及／或醫院名稱 Address(es) 地址 Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) (DD/MM/YYYY) 診治及／或留院日期(日/月/年) 16. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Qualification of Physician 醫生資格 Address 地址 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C22 (11/2025) 2 of 2 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 (DD日/MM月/YYYY年) Tel. No. 電話號碼"});
