window.__KB.push({"t": "Special Request for Hard Copy Policy Contract 特別申請紙本保單合約 Branch Code 分行編號 Adviso", "f": "RC01.pdf", "s": "Special Request for Hard Copy Policy Contract 特別申請紙本保單合約 Branch Code 分行編號 Advisor Code 保險顧問編號 Advisor Name 保險顧問姓名 Location 地點: Points to Note 注意事項 1. Hard Copy Policy contract printing service is only applicable to insurance plan(s) issued within 30 days and issued after Nov 5, 2023. VHIS Basic Plan policies will continue to follow the existing VHIS arrangement, and the above-mentioned handling is not applicable. 編印紙本保單 合約服務只適用於保單簽發日起30天內申請，且保單簽發日期後於2023年11月5日。鑑於自願醫保(VHIS)保單將依據其現時的電子保單合約安 排，故此安排將不適用於自願醫保 (VHIS)保單。 2. Each policy is eligible to maximum one hard copy policy contract printing service. 每份保單最多只享有一次編印紙本保單合約服務。 3. The request is required to be verified and submitted through insurance advisor. 此申請必須經由保險顧問核實及遞交。 4. Turnaround time of contract printing is 14 working days. The printed policy contract once ready, will be delivered to servicing advisor for delivery. 編印紙本保單合約需時14個工作天。而編印好的保單合約將交予保險顧問送遞。 5. Please submit the completed form after policy issuance. In case servicing advisor submitted the form before policy issuance, the request will not be handled. 請在保單生效後才遞交已填妥的表格。如保險顧問在保單生效前已提交表格，此要求將不獲處理。 Policy No. 保單編號 Name of Policyowner 保單持有人姓名 Policy Issue Date 保單簽發日期 Is it the first time to request for hard copy contract printing within 30 days from policy issuance? 這次是否於保單簽發日起30天內第一 次要求印刷紙本保單合約?  Yes 是  No 否 Signature of Policyowner 保單持有人簽署 x Signature of Advisor 保險顧問簽署  The above information has been verified. 上述資料已經本人核對無誤。 x Date 日期: Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 Date 日期: RC01 (12/2025) *OBJTRC01* INTERNAL"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "This is a fillable form. You can fill it in and print it for signature. Print Re", "f": "T01.pdf", "s": "This is a fillable form. You can fill it in and print it for signature. Print Reset Save APPLICATION FOR TERM CONVERSION 定期保險轉換申請書 Branch code 分行編號 Advisor code 保險顧問編號 Advisor's name 保險顧問姓名 Contact no. 聯絡電話 Location 地點 Converted Policy No. 轉換保單編號 Full name of policyowner 保單持有人姓名 Full name of insured 受保人姓名 Important Notes – Please read before ﬁlling in this form 重要事項 ‒ 請於填寫此表格前參閱有關內容 1. This application is applicable for term conversion and should be submitted together with the application form. 此申請書適用於定期保險轉換申請並必須連同 投保申請書一併提交。 2. In application form, “Policy Replacement” and “Cancellation Rights and Refund of Premium(s) and Levy within Cooling-Oﬀ Period” sections are not applicable. For conversion without additional coverage on new policy, the sections on “Medical Evidence of Proposed Insured”, “Other Information of Proposed Insured” and “Health Questions of Proposed Insured” are also not required. Please cross out all the unused sections. 投保申請書內的「轉保」及「冷靜期內取消保單的權利及退還保費及徵費」部份並不適用。如新保單不涉及額外保障，有關 「擬受保人的健康資料」、「擬受保人的其他資料」及「擬受保人的健康狀況」的部份也無須填寫。請刪去所有不適用部份。 3. Please complete this form in English BLOCK letters legibly with policyowner’s signature that corresponds with the company record. Any amendments should be clearly indicated and counter-signed by the policyowner. 請用英文正楷清楚地填寫此表格，並由保單持有人簽署，而簽名必須與本公司檔案相符。任何資料如有更改，保單持有人必須清楚註明並在更改 的位置簽署作實。 4. Manulife shall have the right to update this form from time to time and to accept or reject the form submitted by you if you fail to fulﬁll the Company’s requirements. 宏利有權隨時更 新表格內容，如閣下未能符合本公司的有關規定，宏利將保留接受或拒絕閣下遞交之申請表格的權利。 5. Please read the Notice to Customers relating to the Personal Data (Privacy) Ordinance (\"Notice\") before you complete this form. The Notice is available on Manulife's website (www.manulife.com.hk) or upon request from your Manulife Advisor. By completing and returning to Manulife the form, you are agreeing to the Notice. 當閣下填寫此表格前，請閱畢《有 關〈個人資料(私隱)條例〉的客戶通知》（「通知」）。該通知可於宏利網址 (www.manulife.com.hk) 或向閣下的宏利顧問索取。透過填妥及交回此表格，即表示閣下同意該通知之內容。 CONVERSION DETAILS 轉換資料 The insurance being converted is contained in 此轉換源自 q Individual term policy 個人定期保單 q Others 其他 The conversion is 此轉換為 q Total 全部 q Partial 部份 - $ Converted amount 轉換金額 q Supplementary term beneﬁt provision 附加定期保障條款 to become the basic plan coverage of the new policy 將成為新保單的基本計劃保障 - $ Unconverted amount 不轉換金額 q to become a supplementary beneﬁt of the new policy 將成為新保單的附加保障 - $ Unconverted amount 不轉換金額 q to be continued to remain under the Existing Plan 將繼續於現有計劃內保留 - $ Unconverted amount 不轉換金額 q to be dropped and terminated 將取消並終止 New policy year date 新保單生效日期 DD 日 MM月 YYYY年 Note: The day should be the same as that of the policy year date of the original policy. 註 : 此日必須與原本保單生效日期相同。 Is the policy being converted presently assigned or is any assignment or release of assignment presently being processed? 要轉換的保單是否已轉讓或正在處理轉讓／取消轉讓手續？ q No 否 q Yes 是 (If “Yes”, please give date and details 如答案為「是」，請提供日期及詳細資料 ) DECLARATION 聲明 I/We have read the above statements and answers. They are complete and true to the best of my/our knowledge and belief and form part of the application and the basis of the policy to be issued. I/We have read and fully understood the above Important Notes before signing this form. 本人／吾等已細閱上述聲明與答覆，確信其為真實無訛，並明瞭以上一切資料 將構成保險投保申請書之部份內容並為日後簽發保單之基礎。在簽署此表格前，本人／吾等已細閱以上之重要事項。 IT IS DECLARED, UNDERSTOOD AND AGREED that (1) this application for conversion will form part of the new policy; (2) the insurance being converted will be processed according to the instructions stated in Conversion Details and the new policy will become effective; (3) any assignment now in force relating to the insurance being converted will apply in a like manner to the new policy; (4) if the conversion is such that Manulife requires evidence of insurability, the policyowner’s or life insured’s failure to disclose or misrepresentation of any fact within his/her knowledge that is material to this Application For Term Conversion, any medical evidence form or any written statements or answers furnished as evidence of insurability, will not, in the absence of fraud, render this conversion voidable by Manulife after the new policy has been in force during the life insured’s lifetime for 2 years from the date of issue of the new policy or the date of any reinstatements; (5) if the life insured commits suicide, whether sane or insane before the date 1 year after the date of issue of the new policy or the date of any reinstatements, Manulife’s liability will be limited to the liability had there been no conversion, decreased by the premium which would have been payable had there been no conversion and by any amounts paid by Manulife, and increased by any amounts paid to Manulife, the amounts being those paid because of the conversion and thereafter; (6) the conversion will not become effective until the new policy is delivered to and accepted by the policyowner and the first premium is paid during the life insured’s lifetime and continued insurability under the Company’s rules; (7) I/we declare that I/we do not have any bankruptcy petition made against me/us. 謹此聲明本人／吾等清楚明白及同 意下列各項: (1) 此轉換申請將會成為新保單的一部份；(2) 用作轉換的保單會根據轉換資料一項的指示處理，新的保單將會生效；(3) 任何與此轉換申請有關及已生效的轉讓，均適用 於新保單； (4) 倘需就是次轉換提供受保資格證明，保單持有人或受保人在此「定期保險轉換申請書」、健康證明文件或任何以書面形式或口述提供之受保資格證明中，沒有披露其得 悉之重要資料，而若此轉換由新保單簽發日期或任何復效日期起兩年後，及於受保人在世期間及新保單仍然生效之年，在非欺騙情況下此轉換將不受爭議； (5) 在新保單簽發日期或 任何復效日期起計一年內，若受保人自殺，不論事發時精神是否健全，宏利之責任只限於轉換時及其後繳交之保費，在扣除有關該保單未轉換前應繳付之保費及支出後，予以退還； (6) 新保單送至保單持有人及得其接納、首期保費於受保人在期間繳清及根據本公司條例受保資格不變之情況下，此轉換始會生效；(7) 本人／吾等聲明本人／吾等現時並沒有破產。 Signed on this 簽署日期： X Day 日 day of , Month 月 Year 年 X Signature(s) of irrevocable beneficiary(ies) (if applicable) 不可更改之受益人簽署 (如適用) Signature of collateral assignee (if applicable) 附屬抵押轉讓受讓人簽署 (如適用) X X Signature of witness 見證人簽署 (Name 姓名: ) Signature of policyowner 保單持有人簽署 *OBJTAGECON* *OBJTAGECON* Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 T01 (04/2026) Please aﬃx the new policy no. here 請在此貼上新保單編號 (For oﬃce use only 公司專用)"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "This is a fillable form. You can fill it in and print it for signature. Print Re", "f": "T07_CA.pdf", "s": "This is a fillable form. You can fill it in and print it for signature. Print Reset Save Policy no. DEED / RELEASE OF COLLATERAL ASSIGNMENT Branch code Advisor code Advisor's name Contact no. Location Full name of policyowner Full name of insured (Fill in only if different from policyowner) For Collateral Assignment in accordance with the terms of PART A, please put a “ü ” in the box in PART A and complete the details in PART C. For Release of Collateral Assignment, please put a “ü ” in the box and complete the details in PART B. q PART A : COLLATERAL ASSIGNMENT The policyowner (“assignor”), in consideration of a loan in the amount of dated / / (DD/MM/YYYY) (“the loan”), granted by the following party as stated in PART C (“assignee”), hereby assigns the rights and interests in the above policy to the assignee as collateral security for the repayment of the outstanding amount of the loan subject to the following conditions: (i) If the assignor shall well and truly pay, or cause to be paid, to the assignee, the loan together with the prescribed interest thereon, the assignee shall reassign the policy and the benefit obtained under this Collateral Assignment to the assignor. (ii) Before the release of this Collateral Assignment, no further beneficiary designation shall be made without the approval of the assignee. All existing beneficiary(ies) designation and any further beneficiary(ies) designation as approved by the assignee shall be amended in such a manner that the assignee shall have the first right to receive any proceeds of the policy payable to the beneficiary, having priority over all such beneficiaries up to the outstanding amount of the loan (including interest). (iii)The assignor shall retain the right to surrender the policy and borrow policy loan with the approval of the assignee. Save for the above, the assignor shall retain the right without the need of approval from the assignee to the receipt of dividends or coupons. (iv)Should the assignor die before the release of this Collateral Assignment, the assignee shall be entitled to exercise his/her rights hereunder and any proceeds or benefits payable to the assignee under the policy exceeding the outstanding amount of the loan (including interest) shall be returned to the last beneficiary designated and Manulife is hereby authorized to distribute the said proceeds and benefits on behalf of the assignee accordingly. (v) A receipt signed by the assignee, his/her executors, administrators shall in all cases, fully discharge Manulife from its liabilities and obligations under the above policy in respect of which receipt is given. (vi)This policy cannot be wholly or partially assigned again without the release of this Collateral Assignment. POINTS TO NOTE ABOUT COLLATERAL ASSIGNMENT: I/We confirm that I/we fully understand the risks, implications and limitations associated with pledging or assigning my insurance policy as collateral, including but not limited to the following (as applicable). 1. Stand-alone arrangement/contract: Any loan facility acquired through pledging or assigning the policy as collateral is a stand-alone arrangement between you and the lender. It is not, and does not form part of the insurance contract between you and Manulife (International) Limited (the “Insurer”). The Insurer is not a party to the loan contract or policy assignment agreement or other similar agreements and is therefore not governed by the terms and conditions (including dispute resolution) of these contract and agreement you enter into with the lender. In case you have any questions about the terms and conditions, you should contact the lender. 2. Restriction of rights under the policy: All or part of your rights under the policy will be assigned to the lender as collateral via a deed of assignment. Subject to the terms and conditions of the loan contract and policy assignment agreement, the lender will be entitled to exercise all or part of the rights under your policy, and you will not be able to exercise those rights unless the lender’s approval is obtained. Examples of those rights include: • receive any benefits (including surrender value, death benefit, etc. ) payable by the insurer under your policy; • cancel your policy within the cooling off period, surrender the policy, or make withdrawals; • apply for policy loan, or exercise any options under the policy; and • make certain changes or amendments to your policy (e.g. appointment of new beneficiary, further pledge or assign the policy). You should therefore carefully read the terms and conditions of the loan contract and policy assignment agreement, and consider how these potential adverse impacts may affect the outcome of the policy and whether the policy is still suitable for you. 3. Shortfall in actual benefits receivable: The actual net benefits receivable under the policy pledged or assigned as collateral for a loan facility would be less than the amount indicated in the relevant Benefit Illustration, as part of the benefit payments would be offset by the repayment of the loan facility (including the principal amount of the loan and the relevant interest). Depending on the amount of loan (including the principal amount of the loan and the relevant interest) and the terms and conditions of the loan contract and policy assignment agreement, this shortfall may be significant. 4. Release and access of information: The lender will be given rights to access your policy information and may from time to time instruct the Insurer to release information relating to your policy, for example, surrender value, cash value, and any loans or advances on the policy. 5. Risk of collateral top-up and repayment on demand: Where your policy is pledged or assigned as collateral for a loan facility, your loan facility may be subject to review by the lender and the lender has the right to restructure or terminate the loan facility at any time. The lender may request you to provide additional collater"});
